messages.content: What is one of the features provided by the image_control custom node in ComfyUI?
One of the features provided by the image_control custom node in ComfyUI is inpainting with LaMa.
Yes, image_control supports outpainting using the LaMa model.
Can image_control be used to resize images?
Yes, image_control provides a feature to resize images by zooming in or out.
How does image_control handle the issue of the pelvis becoming enlarged when generating images with large breasts?
image_control has solved the problem of the pelvis becoming enlarged when printing huge breasts by using the 'Change Breast' feature.
Does image_control have a feature for generating images with low-rise or low-leg pants?
Yes, image_control provides a feature for generating images with low-rise (low-leg) pants.
Can image_control create images with see-through clothes?
Yes, image_control has a feature that allows for generating images with see-through clothes.
Is it possible to resize only the head of a subject using image_control?
Yes, image_control offers a feature called 'Resize Head' that allows users to resize only the head of a subject in an image.
Does image_control support generating images that show only one breast?
Yes, image_control has a feature that enables generating images showing only one breast.
